window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Once upon a time, in a parallel universe, there existed the continent of Triton....</p> <p><i>The Beast has risen!</i></p> <p>Airen is at war. The queen is dead. The coven is incomplete. And things are uncertain under the sea.</p> <p>Now, the unicorns and mermaids and witches and warriors and the strangers from other lands all must band together to face the Beast and save Triton.</p> <p>The unions have been realized. Silence and Mars, True and Farah, Cassius and Elena, and Aramus and Ha-Lah are at their fullest powers.</p> <p>But the gods require sacrifice. The sacrifice of pure love. If it isnâ€™t given, the Beast will prevail, and Triton will fall.</p> <p>It cannot be escaped; they must use all their might and magic....</p> <p><b>The Rising is nigh!</b></p>"; 
